<br>
If you dont, dont bother going.  If you do, you'll be fine. <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.cox.net/mherlihy/img/gallerus.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--><br>
<!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=412980" target="top">Lorcann</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->   <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=412968" target="top">Gallerus</a><!--EZCODE LINK END-->   <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=413004" target="top">Borstal</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=odiussilvertongue>OdiusSilvertongue</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 77<br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/17/03 11:27 am)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Halls of Training - Am I ready?</span><hr size=1> As mentioned above, without a level 60 person tanking you can not use taunt to gain aggro.  So aggro procs are going to be the only way to gain aggro.  Taunt may not be the greatest skill but life is much harder without it.  Anyone remember revised CT before the taunt fix? <p><B><a href= http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=81233><FONT SIZE="-1">Vladimoir</a></FONT></B>
<BR>
<i><FONT SIZE="-6">Overlord</i></FONT><br>

