<br>
- Just build agro long enough until you want the guild coming in and you should be fine - rest of the guild can hide from AE while you are building agro<br>
- AC/HP gear<br>
- Having a bard with AE resists helps a lot.<br>
- Make sure you can slow them (lvl 54 shammy won't do)<br>
- If you get a Vehement or Ancient Wyvern, use your disc - they are mean.<br>
- To avoid gaters, have chanters cast Torment of Argli and manasieve. Gaters are white wurms and some of the drakes (I believe all but the red ones)<br>
- The green drakes cast an uncurable slow (lasts about 15mins). Have your bard play PR/DR when you have one of them incoming.<br>
- Don't let the mobs get too close to the door - open or not, the outside mobs will assist. (sitting casters near door on a pull are disastrous) <p><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=26345">Merrahar</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
