<br>
Anything anyone else says is wishful thinking.  You can't solo a mob for very long before you need a slow.  the level 63+ stuff assrapes me for 390's consistently while evasive.  You're not going to have the time you need to generate enough aggro to hold it without someone slowing that mob, taking aggro and dying.<br>
